      "text": "（サニーピースのライブ当日。開演の直前）\n（俺は一人一人に声をかけていた……最後は雫だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(On the day of a Sunny Peace live‚ right before curtain up‚)\n(I spoke to each of them individually. Shizuku is the last.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.544186135225518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……ふにっ……んふっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*squeeze* *squeeze*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.350000190734864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.350000190734866
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.100000190734832
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "どうした、雫？\nさっきから鏡に向かって何してるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ what’s up?\nWhy have you been sitting in front of the mirror for so long?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.166666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.521723556518594
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.764768321563807
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "顔の、マッサージ……自然な笑顔\n作れるように……やわらかくしてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Massaging… my face‚ to make it softer\nand get a natural smile…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.764768321563807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.908480930328412
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、そういうことか\n大丈夫、いい表情になってきてるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I see.\nDon’t worry about it‚ you’re looking good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.882238375147192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.06811818168278
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "ん……うれしい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m glad…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.06811818168278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.41811820552468
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ところで……もうすぐ出番だけど\n調子はどうだ？　緊張してないか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ you’re on in a minute‚\nbut are you feeling okay? Are you stressed out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫……\nむしろ、今は、楽しみ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m okay…\nActually‚ I’m looking forward to it now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.989955153919375
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "みんなも一緒、だし……\nたくさん、練習……してきたので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because I’ll be with everyone…\nand we’ve been rehearsing… so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.88995524928683
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。みんな一緒だし、これまでの練習は\n雫を裏切らない。だから、楽しんでくるといいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. You’re all together‚ and all your rehearsals\nare your foundation. So‚ go out there and have fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.99750773331126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "はい……\nがんばって、楽しんで……きます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay…\nI’ll do my best and… have some fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6267.324621336826,
          "startTime": 67.46732462133683
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.41732462133682
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.41732462133682
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "雫、お疲れ様！\n凄くいいステージだったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ you did great out there!\nYou were awesome on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.72527767206942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……はあ……\nちゃんと……できてた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff*\nDid I do… okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.91282627510854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、最高だったよ\nここまで聞こえるファンの声援が、何よりの証拠だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ you were excellent.\nBut the best proof of that is the noise of the fans. You can hear them from here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.37949294177515,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3153.8403915581766,
          "startTime": 81.53333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.4128262751085
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "……すごい……今まで……私\nアイドルを、応援する側、だったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Amazing… I… never…\nI was always on the side of the fans…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5128262751085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.90616354895457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "こんな声の中で……\nステージ、立ってたんだな、って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never knew that…\nidols …stood on stage facing this commotion…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、不思議……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels a bit surreal…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.11616610455718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.32668759592582
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "雫も、すっかりステージに立つ側だからな\nそんな風に感じるのも……ん、涙？　どうした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And now‚ Shizuku‚ you’re on the stage side.\nSo feeling like that is… Huh? You’re crying? What’s wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.29335426259246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.40673329599903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "……え……なんで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Why am I?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.40673329599905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.40673329599905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（流れる涙に自分でも気付いてなかったのか）\n（でも、理由は悲しいからではないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Did she not notice her own flowing tears?)\n(But she wasn’t crying out of sadness.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.473399962666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しいことがあったんだよな？\n今日のステージで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something happened to make you happy‚ didn’t it?\nSomething happy on stage today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.70673329599909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "……うん\nあった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah.\nIt did…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "私の、ソロパート……入って\nコンサートライトが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I started my solo part‚\nall the glow sticks…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_03-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "私の色で……いっぱいに、なった時",
      "translations": {
        "en": "flickered… in my color.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.02473137893497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
